Lectura del mapa

30 de mayo de 2018

  • Obtener el mapa de la Universidad Nacional.
  • Obtener el mapa de Medellín

Obtener el mapa de la Universidad Nacional.

library(ggmap)
## Loading required package: ggplot2
un <- get_map(location = c(lon = -75.576807, lat = 6.262117),
               zoom = 18,
              maptype = "hybrid")
## Map from URL : http://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=6.262117,-75.576807&zoom=18&size=640x640&scale=2&maptype=hybrid&language=en-EN&sensor=false
ggmap(un, extent = "normal")

save(un, file = "un.RData")
rm(un)

Obtener el mapa de Medellín

medellin <- get_map(location = c(lon = -75.576807, lat = 6.262117),
               zoom = 12,
              maptype = "hybrid")
## Map from URL : http://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=6.262117,-75.576807&zoom=12&size=640x640&scale=2&maptype=hybrid&language=en-EN&sensor=false
ggmap(medellin, extent = "normal")

save(medellin, file = "medellin.RData")
rm(medellin)
